     * FAQ

     * FAQ
       New Site
       New Domain
       Http://tdupp6lmgnpex5ss.onion
       New Email
       thepotshop@torbox3uiot6wchz.onion
       Why the new site?
       Our old site was getting slow and clients were complain that the
       site was not as secure as it could be. We are introducing a new PGP
       email system where all our emails will now be sent via PGP
       Encryption. The previous host did not take kindly to our growing
       business and delete our site. We now have better hosting and better
       security.
       With the los of our old site we have lost our user database but all
       outstanding orders have been saved via email. and 90% of them has
       been shipped.
       We will be continuing to update our site in the comming weeks to
       make it the best Pot Site on the TOR network.
       We hope you enjoy our new site !!!
       Shipping
       Shipping is done on Mondays Wednesdays and Fridays
       New Shipping Charges
       USA     :   $ 6.95
       UK       :   $ 9.95
       Other  :   $ 12.95
       All orders more than $100 will receive Free Shipping
       Products are double sealed and package does not have any markings
       on them to give suspicion to the content.
       We have a 95% Success rate shipping our products. If a client does
       not receive their package in 30 days we will reship it for $ 6.95
       We have shipped 750 Products sins the start of our shop more than a
       year ago.
       We aim to please and try our utmost to keep our clients happy
       Email : thepotshop@torbox3uiot6wchz.onion
       Payment
       We try to keep all our payments as secure as possible. For the
       safety of our clients. We only use BITCOIN! No other payment
       methods are available!
       Payments takes an hour to reflect onto our account and the system
       will then mark the status of the order as processing you will not
       receive an confirmation email when payment has be received but will
       receive an update as soon as your product has been shipped.
       Info
       All our products are sourced from the best growers in the business!
       We do grow our own we buy in bulk and aim to bring you the best
       product at the best price.

   [3260]View Cart “Volcano Plenty Vaporizer” has been added to your cart.
   [3261]Capture

Arizer Air Vaporizer

   $149.95
   Category: [3262]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3263]Description

Product Description

   Ultra-compact, lightweight, easy to operate & maintain, and completely
   portable, the Arizer Air features a high quality ceramic heating
   element, high quality glass dishes, and high quality rechargeable,
   interchangeable lithium batteries.

   Offering an hour of continuous use per charge, plus the ability to use
   the unit while charging the battery, and the option to have spare
   batteries fully charged, the Arizer Air is ideal for day to day use at
   home and on the go!

   Utilizing a sleek and compact design concept, the Arizer Air measures
   122mm in height and 29mm in diameter, conveniently fitting inside the
   palm of your hand, pockets, or purse. A solid shell protects the Arizer
   Air from general wear and tear and a vented top keeps the surface
   temperature of the body cool.

   The Arizer Air portable diffuser is equipped with a 1-2 minute warm up
   time, an advanced temperature control system with 5 settings, and a
   built-in automatic shut off safety setting after 10 minutes of
   operation.

   Arizer Air Temperature Levels: Level 1 (Blue) – 180°C / 356°F, Level 2
   (White) – 190°C / 374°F, Level 3 (Green) – 200°C / 392°F, Level 4
   (Orange) – 205°C / 401°F, Level 5 (Red) – 210°C / 410°F.

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Charger / Power adapter
     * 2 x Glass diffuser stems
     * 1 x Glass aroma dish
     * 1 x Clear protective silicone skin
     * 1 x Stainless steel stirring tool
     * 1 x Carrying case

   [3297]White-Berry-Marijuana-Bud

Berry White 10g

   [DEL: $29.95 :DEL] [INS: $19.95 :INS]
   Category: [3298]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3299]Description

Product Description

   Berry White is a hybrid strain that is the offspring of parents of
   near-celebrity status in the cannabis world: Blueberry and White Widow.
   Berry is famous in its own right for its even, balanced effects that
   offer relaxation from stress and anxiety along with a sense of
   euphoria. This strain is perfect for inspiring an upbeat mood and may
   lead to conversation and creative pursuits. This plant’s flowers have a
   light sour berry and pine smell and a fresh taste similar to their
   scent. They generally have a strong blue coloring contrasted by orange
   hairs.

   [3333]black-label-kush

Black Label Kush 10G

   $24.95

   This lesser-known strain is a classic indica that provides patients
   with reliable and lengthy pain and stress relief. The effects
   transition from light and floaty to the heavy sedation typical of
   indica plants. Black Label Kush has a strong pungence bordering on the
   harsh side, but provides a rich medicating experience.
   SKU: 003Bck. Category: [3334]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3335]Description

Product Description

   Black Label Kush
   Black Label Kush is a heavy indica that is great for sleep and
   relaxation. Black Label Kush is the type of bud that will allow you to
   slow down and not get so stressed out about the small things in life.
   Black Label Kush is a combination of two Afghani varieties and is also
   good for pain relief. Black Label Kush is not a common strain, so if
   you get your hands on it, consider yourself lucky.

   “Grade: A+

   Type: Indica

   Looks: “Medium” sized, very dense, evergreen marijuana nuggets with
   complete frosty trich coverage with areas of dark (purple) leaf
   coverage andnoticeable “rust/red hair.”

   Smell: A crisp sharp scent of pine and menthol.

   Taste: A very “rich” evergreen (and slight hint of fruitiness) danky
   mouth feel with a thick/rich hash like after taste.

   Buzz Type: A very heavy/floaty and slightly euphoric high. Provided me
   with relaxation and pain relief.

   Buzz Length: Above Average to Very Long (1.5 hours to 2+ hours)

   Summary:

   A very nice Indica strain, this batch Black Label had some super FROSTY
   marijuana nuggets. The taste was “rich” as if taking a skillet hit of
   wax. Big sniffs cleared out my nostrils as the scent was very “sharp”
   when wafting the container up to my nose.

   The first night I had a session with Black Label, I was couch locked.
   This strain gave me the feeling if eyes were “crossed.” My head felt
   “light” at the start of this buzz. The feeling I experienced is like
   “floating on clouds.” I know it’s a long time “stoner cliche,” but the
   wording does fit. The feeling of “lightness” progresses more into the
   “heavy;” especially around the eyes, about half hour after ending a
   session. This strain provided lots of “body tingle and pressure.”
   Again, this was mostly confined around the eyes and very prevalent in
   nostril area.

   Black Label was an excellent pain relief and chill out strain. This
   strain was very good at slowing my “racing mind” down. I big side
   effect was dry/sticky mouth. I did not so much get the munchies, but I
   got very thirsty with this strain. I had a big craving for sweet tea as
   I found myself in the McDonald’s drive thru many times to quench my
   thirst with their dollar sweet tea.

   Black Label is a nice strain to relax and “veg” out with and watch late
   night television while easing into a good sleep. Most of the time, I
   eased into a good nights sleep (70%) vs. being put in a state of couch
   lock (30%).”

Indore Blue Dream 10G

   $24.95

   Blue Dream, a sativa-dominant hybrid originating in California, has
   achieved legendary status among West Coast strains. Crossing a
   Blueberry indica with the sativa Haze, Blue Dream balances full-body
   relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration. Novice and veteran
   consumers alike enjoy the level effects of Blue Dream, which ease you
   gently into a calm euphoria. Some Blue Dream phenotypes express a more
   indica-like look and feel, but the sativa-leaning variety remains most
   prevalent.
   SKU: 004Bd. Category: [3370]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3371]Description

Product Description

   Blue Dream

   You will find Blue Dream listed as a Sativa strain on most dispensary
   menus throughout California because of the strong, energetic head-high
   it is known for. However, digging deeper you will find that the actual
   Blue Dream genetics can be linked to Blueberry and Super Silver Haze,
   making it a 50/50 hybrid strain of cannabis. This explains why patients
   experience a nice full-body high from the Blueberry (Indica), but also
   a powerful cerebral experience from its Haze (Sativa) genetic
   counterparts.

   Blue Dream (Hybrid) Stems From Blueberry and Haze
   Being a 50/50 hybrid, you get the best of both worlds with this strain
   of cannabis. The effects are instant & plentiful, making it an instant
   favorite among most MMJ patients. However, as with all strains of
   cannabis, the specific phenotype you are medicating with is unique and
   has its own characteristics.
   For this reason, it’s important to remember that not all Blue Dream
   cuts will make you feel happy, energetic, with a soaring head-high.
   Although common, this is not always the case. Rather, depending on the
   Blue Dream phenotype, people may experience more of a full body melt
   (Indica-dominant) or uplifting head high (Sativa-dominant). It really
   depends on the specific phenotype you are medicating with. Like people,
   all strains of cannabis have their unique differences.

   Having said that, I will say that Blue Dream typically seems to have
   the same overall characteristics, regardless of phenotype. Generally
   speaking, the Blue Dream strain is popular for removing all types of
   stress and anxiety. Its calming mind-warp is a staple for the strain
   that is prominent in even the strongest Indica-dominant batches of Blue
   Dream I have come across.
   Long, thick, tan hairs are common when visually inspecting the Blue
   Dream strain. The smell is always rich, with a subtle sugar-cookie
   funk. This particular batch of Blue Dream has really frosty buds
   covered in so many sparkling trichomes that it made the overall
   appearance of the buds seem lighter in color. The vapor from the Blue
   Dream strain is super smooth, coating the entire mouth with a sweet
   blueberry sugar taste on the exhale.

   Final Thoughts About The Blue Dream Cannabis Strain
   It’s one of my go-to strains for a relaxing, thought-provoking, and
   stress-free experience. This hybrid strain seems to make the day’s
   endless list of things to do seem much more attainable. The effects
   generated from Blue Dream are typically long lasting, euphoric, and can
   be full-bodied depending on the cut of Blue Dream you have.
   Considered a personal favorite of most patients I speak to, Blue Dream
   is definitely a medical marijuana strain that is sure to grow in
   popularity for years to come.

   have created a masterpiece with their Elite model. Featuring precision
   temperature control and an integrated pump, this vaporizer offers four
   vaping methods for you to choose from: via the whip, direct inhalation,
   bag inflation and water pipe glass adapter.

   It’s not just fun to show off, though. The digital readout shows you
   the exact temperature your dry herbs are being utilized at. This allows
   you to find the perfect temp for all different varieties of flower
   without risking burning or having a bad experience.

   Made for both beginners and experts alike, the Herbal Aire Elite
   Vaporizer delivers premium vapor clouds with minimal fuss. The whole
   system is easy to use and adapt, with simple connections for the
   various attachments and inhalation methods. You can switch out to your
   favorite style of vaping in just a moment!

KandyPens K-Vape Micro-DX Vaporizer Pen

   $99.95
   Category: [3797]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3798]Description

Product Description

   The K-Vape Micro-DX by KandyPens is a Micro-Digital vaporizer that has
   been specially designed to utilize convection heating while remaining
   user friendly and small enough to fit in the palm of your hand. The
   K-Vape Micro-DX pen uses True Convection Technology™ meaning no
   combustion or smoke, just perfect vapor as hot air passes over the herb
   filled chamber to generate pure vapor.

   This great vape pen comes with a large anodized aluminum chamber that
   can hold up to 0.5 grams of dry herbs and has a fast heat-up time with
   over 80 available temperature settings ranging from 350°F – 430°F. The
   temperature settings can be seen on the pens digital OLED display along
   with the word heat when heating up and the word warm when the desired
   temperature has been reached. This vaporizer pen allows you to
   fine-tune your vaping experience to get that optimal heat level to
   produce thick, dense clouds with consistent results. The vape pen even
   has Smart Memory Technology that remembers your ideal settings and will
   heat the device to the last temperature used.

   For safety the K-Vape Micro-DX Pen has a 5 minute auto-shut off feature
   that ensures that your device turns off automatically to avoid any
   potentially dangerous situations. Charging the K-Vape Micro-DX has been
   made easy, simply attach the provided retractable charger cable to a
   universal USB connection and your device will start to power up
   immediately. Along with the micro USB cord, you will also find a
   cleaning brush, and a metal scoop all packed perfectly into the pens
   slide open display box.

   The K-Vape Micro-DX pen has a 3 hour battery life and is made from
   durable plastic that not only looks great, it also keeps your hands
   cool, making it even easier to hold and use. As an added bonus, this
   great dry herbal vaporizer comes with a lifetime warranty, so if you re
   looking for a top performing, portable digital vaporizer, then the
   KandyPens K-Vape Micro-DX Vaporizer is a perfect choice for new or more
   experienced vape smokers

   [3868]SUPER-LEMON-HAZE

Lemon Haze 100G

   $199.95

   Lemon Haze has been characterized as smelling of fresh peeled lemon
   slices with a similar taste. Its buds appear to be green and yellow
   with amber hairs on the trichomes, giving it the yellow tint. This
   strain’s THC has been measured at about 15-20% with a CBD of 0.38%.
   SKU: 002Lh. Category: [3869]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [3870]Description

Product Description

   Lemon Haze = Lemon Skunk x Silver Haze
   Digging a layer deeper, you will find that the Lemon Skunk found in
   Lemon Haze is a cross hatch between two Skunk plants with phenotypes
   chosen specifically for their zesty lemon characteristics. This
   explains where the lemon-peel stench comes from. With a Lemon mother,
   which has been kept in Vegas for over 20 years, and a father
   hand-picked by DNA Genetics in Holland, you know you are getting one
   heavy hitting cannabis strain.

   Additionally, the Lemon Skunk strain is known to be a good yielder that
   will grow tall with a high calyx ratio, like most Cannabis Sativa
   strains. The influence of Lemon Skunk is apparent in this batch of
   Lemon Haze, with its great smelling buds that are green with thick
   orange hairs. When I spoke with the growers, they recommended cutting
   it down between 50 – 56 days for the sweetest and tastiest cannabinoid
   profile.
   The Silver Haze strain, on the other hand, stems from a cross of Haze
   with Northern Lights and Skunk. Familiar to many as a buzzing head
   high, the Silver Haze strain is zone-inducing and extremely relaxing.
   Silver Haze gets its name from the massive amount of shiny trichomes
   covering the buds. The strong high leaves you feeling happy and clear
   headed — making it a popular choice among many patients dealing with
   anxiety disorders such as PTSD

   Flavors

   Lemon Citrus Sweet

   [4277]super-silver-haze

Super Silver Haze 5G

   $9.95

   Super Silver Haze was the first prize winner at the High Times Cannabis
   Cup in 1997, 1998, and 1999. It also won awards at the High
   Times Harvest Festival. By crossing the genetics of Skunk,Northern
   Lights, and Haze, we are left with a beautiful, sticky sativa blend
   that boasts anenergetic, long-lasting body high. The uplifting effects
   are a great remedy for high stress levels or when suffering from a lack
   of appetite or nausea.
   SKU: 001SSH. Category: [4278]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [4279]Description

Product Description

   Super Silver Haze: (Skunk X Haze) X (Northern Lights X Haze)
   The Skunk, Northern Lights, and Haze strains combine forces to give the
   Super Silver strain star-studded genetics. It is a Sativa-dominant
   hybrid that has become one of the building blocks for superior cannabis
   since it was released in the 90’s.
   The Super Silver Haze strain really rose to fame at the end of the 20th
   Century, when it won the HIGH TIMES Cannabis Cup three years in a row.
   The strain was under the care of Green House Seeds at that point, but
   the company’s co-founders split soon thereafter.

   Since all phenotypes of cannabis strains will have different
   characteristics, it is important to remember that your batch of Super
   Silver Haze may be slightly more Indica-dominant or Sativa-dominant.
   Still, many differences are small and only noticeable to the
   experienced cannabis connoisseur.
   For instance, the terpenoid profiles will be different for each batch
   of Super Silver Haze, likely due to differences in grow environment.
   Still, this can sometimes result in a situation in which the patient
   may not know what to expect.

   The smell of Super Silver Haze can vary greatly, depending on which
   phenotype you have. Most often, the strain will be reminiscent of
   earthy haze with undertones of fruity skunk, which translates to
   pleasurable, sweet-tasting vapor that will have you excited for another
   hit.

   I’ve found that the Super Silver Haze strain often provides a whirlwind
   of energy, while producing a calming, uplifting, clear-headed feeling
   of content. For this reason, I would easily consider this one of my
   favorite Sativa-dominant hybrids to start the day.
   Super Silver Haze is considered to be good for headaches, migraines,
   and helping to manage anxiety, although more anecdotal research is
   necessary to know exactly what sort of relief it can offer each
   individual. But not to worry, we’re working on it.

   Flavors

   Sweet, Citrus, Pungent

Cart

     * [4308]Accessories
     * [4309]Cannabis / Weed
     * [4310]Edibles

     * [4312]Vaporizers

   [4313]View Cart “KandyPens K-Vape Micro-DX Vaporizer Pen” has been
   added to your cart.
   [4314]Capture

Storz & Bickel Crafty Vaporizer

   $199.95
   Category: [4315]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [4316]Description
     * [4317]Reviews (0)

Product Description

   The Crafty is a portable, battery-powered Pocket-Vaporizer. The
   Crafty’s compact construction with a single Lithium-Ion battery power
   is complemented by a practical one button control: You turn on the
   Crafty with only one keypress. It then heats up automatically until it
   reaches the default set basic temperature of 356°F (180°C). With a
   double-click on the button, you activate the booster temperature of
   383°F (195°C). When the set vaporization temperature is reached, it is
   signaled through a short double-vibration and the LED-indicator lamp:
   The LED changes the color from red to green.

   With the Crafty, vaporization functions on the basis of a full hot air
   convection heating combined with conduction. The convection heating
   provides an immediate and continuous vaporization, whereas the
   conduction ensures that there is vapor created from the very first
   breath.

   The filling chamber, which is integrated into the vaporizer, is to be
   filled with plant material (this is facilitated by the included filling
   aid) and the cooling unit with mouthpiece is to be attached. The
   cooling unit makes sure that the vapor cools down and guarantees
   optimal flavor and a rich aroma. The Crafty is the smallest Storz &
   Bickel Vaporizer with a size of 4.3 x 2.2 x 1.3 inches (11.0 x 5.7 x
   3.3 cm) and a weight of 0.3 lbs (135 g) and comes with a Crafty
   vaporizer, USB Charger, Filling aid, Grinder, Cleaning brush, Liquid
   pad, 3x spare screens, Set of spare sealing rings and Instruction
   manual.

   The free Crafty Bluetooth Remote Control App offers you the opportunity
   to set basic and booster temperature of your device according to your
   personal preferences. Amongst other things, the App allows you to read
   off the battery charge status on your smartphone, to turn on and off
   the vibration function of the Crafty and to activate an alarm and
   vibration function for your smartphone. You can download the Crafty
   Remote Control App for free from the Apple App Store or from the Google
   Play Store

   [4350]Capture

Volcano Mighty Portable Vaporizer

   $150.00
   Category: [4351]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [4352]Description

Product Description

   The Mighty by Storz & Bickel, is a portable, battery powered and
   dynamic Vaporizer. Due to the plus-/minus keys and the easily visible
   LED-display, the operation of the Mighty is self-explaining: As soon as
   the actual temperature corresponds to the individually adjustable set
   temperature, the device is ready for use. This is additionally
   indicated by a short double-vibration. Through the setting options
   directly on the device, the personally preferred temperature can be
   adjusted gradually during vaporization. The Mighty Vaporizer has a
   Dual-Lithium-Ion battery power, which allows a long operating life and
   a great radius of action. The Mighty can also be operated via power
   adapter with completely discharged batteries.

   With the Mighty, vaporization functions on the basis of a full hot air
   convection heating combined with conduction. The convection heating
   provides an immediate and continuous vaporization, whereas the
   conduction ensures that there is vapor created from the very first
   breath.

   You can use the included filling aid for a quick and clean filling of
   the filling chamber, which is integrated into the vaporizer. In place
   of the cooling unit, the filling aid is attached on top of the filling
   chamber. The cooling unit assures that the vapor cools down and
   guarantees an optimal flavor and a rich aroma.

   The Mighty is a portable, battery-run and powerful Vaporizer by Storz &
   Bickel with a size of 5.5 x 3.2 x 1.2 inches (14.0 x 8.0 x 3.0 cm) and
   a weight of only 0.5 lbs (235 g).

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Power Adapter
     * 1 x Liquid Pad
     * 3 x Spare Screens
     * 1 x Cleaning Brush
     * 1 x Herb Mill (Grinder)
     * 1 x Filling Aid
     * 1 x Seal Rings
     * 1 x Instruction Manual

   [4386]Capture

Volcano Plenty Vaporizer

   $199.95
   Category: [4387]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [4388]Description

Product Description

   The Volcano Plenty Vaporizer is a powerful and sturdy portable device.
   The heat exchanger is equipped with a double helix to ensure efficient
   air heating and quality vaporization. The Volcano Plenty Vaporizer
   features a stainless steel cooling coil, ensuring you a pleasant
   aromatic experience.

   The temperature of the Volcano Plenty can be manually adjusted from
   130°C (266°F) to 202°C (395°F). An analog thermometer shows the
   temperature in the filling chamber, so you can always keep a close eye
   on the temperature. The Volcano Plenty’s bi-metallic regulator ensures
   safe operation, with independent temperature control and automatic
   shut-off.

The benefits of the Volcano vaporization method:

     * Effect
     * Purity
     * Flavor

   The Volcano Vaporization System releases flavors and active ingredients
   from plant material through vaporization by hot air. With the
   vaporization technique hot air passes through the plants. During this
   process the flavoring and active ingredients will be set free through
   controlled temperature 130°C (266°F) to 202°C (395°F). Due to the
   specific vaporization temperature of the plant material the ingredients
   are released into the air and can subsequently be inhaled.

   Smoking or incensing releases ingredients through heat but the
   temperature is reached through combustion which has several
   disadvantages. Smoking involves the combustion, incensing the
   carbonization of plant material, followed by the unavoidable inhalation
   of toxic combustion by-products, which cause irritation of the
   respiratory tract as well as noxious odors. In addition, the high and
   uncontrolled combustion temperature causes the unnecessary destruction
   of the majority of the ingredients, squandering the original material
   without any effect.

   Vaporizing does the opposite, the ingredients are released in a gentle
   way and therefore you enjoy both health benefits as well as economic
   benefits. The plant material doesn’t get burned and hence it is
   possible to vaporize the contents of the filling chamber several times
   until all the aroma and ingredients are completely dissolved.

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Herbal Filling Chamber
     * 1 x Mouthpiece
     * 3 x Normal Screen Set
     * 2 x Tubing (Short)
     * 2 x Tubing (Long)
     * 1 x Cooling Coil
     * 1 x Liquid Pad
     * 1 x Cleaning Brush
     * 1 x Herbal Grinder
     * 1 x Instruction Manual

       New Site
       New Domain
       Http://tdupp6lmgnpex5ss.onion

       thepotshop@torbox3uiot6wchz.onion
       Why the new site?
       Our old site was getting slow and clients were complain that the
       site was not as secure as it could be. We are introducing a new PGP
       email system where all our emails will now be sent via PGP
       Encryption. The previous host did not take kindly to our growing
       business and delete our site. We now have better hosting and better
       security.
       With the los of our old site we have lost our user database but all
       outstanding orders have been saved via email. and 90% of them has
       been shipped.
       We will be continuing to update our site in the comming weeks to
       make it the best Pot Site on the TOR network.
       We hope you enjoy our new site !!!
       Shipping
       Shipping is done on Mondays Wednesdays and Fridays
       New Shipping Charges
       USA     :   $ 6.95
       UK       :   $ 9.95
       Other  :   $ 12.95
       All orders more than $100 will receive Free Shipping
       Products are double sealed and package does not have any markings
       on them to give suspicion to the content.
       We have a 95% Success rate shipping our products. If a client does
       not receive their package in 30 days we will reship it for $ 6.95
       We have shipped 750 Products sins the start of our shop more than a
       year ago.
       We aim to please and try our utmost to keep our clients happy
       Email : thepotshop@torbox3uiot6wchz.onion
       Payment
       We try to keep all our payments as secure as possible. For the
       safety of our clients. We only use BITCOIN! No other payment
       methods are available!
       Payments takes an hour to reflect onto our account and the system
       will then mark the status of the order as processing you will not
       receive an confirmation email when payment has be received but will
       receive an update as soon as your product has been shipped.

       All our products are sourced from the best growers in the business!
       We do grow our own we buy in bulk and aim to bring you the best
       product at the best price.

Arizer Air Vaporizer

   $149.95
   Category: [7657]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [7658]Description

Product Description

   Ultra-compact, lightweight, easy to operate & maintain, and completely
   portable, the Arizer Air features a high quality ceramic heating
   element, high quality glass dishes, and high quality rechargeable,
   interchangeable lithium batteries.

   Offering an hour of continuous use per charge, plus the ability to use
   the unit while charging the battery, and the option to have spare
   batteries fully charged, the Arizer Air is ideal for day to day use at
   home and on the go!

   Utilizing a sleek and compact design concept, the Arizer Air measures
   122mm in height and 29mm in diameter, conveniently fitting inside the
   palm of your hand, pockets, or purse. A solid shell protects the Arizer
   Air from general wear and tear and a vented top keeps the surface
   temperature of the body cool.

   The Arizer Air portable diffuser is equipped with a 1-2 minute warm up
   time, an advanced temperature control system with 5 settings, and a
   built-in automatic shut off safety setting after 10 minutes of
   operation.

   Arizer Air Temperature Levels: Level 1 (Blue) – 180°C / 356°F, Level 2
   (White) – 190°C / 374°F, Level 3 (Green) – 200°C / 392°F, Level 4
   (Orange) – 205°C / 401°F, Level 5 (Red) – 210°C / 410°F.

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Charger / Power adapter
     * 2 x Glass diffuser stems
     * 1 x Glass aroma dish
     * 1 x Clear protective silicone skin
     * 1 x Stainless steel stirring tool
     * 1 x Carrying case

Berry White 10g

   [DEL: $29.95 :DEL] [INS: $19.95 :INS]
   Category: [7693]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [7694]Description

Product Description

   Berry White is a hybrid strain that is the offspring of parents of
   near-celebrity status in the cannabis world: Blueberry and White Widow.
   Berry is famous in its own right for its even, balanced effects that
   offer relaxation from stress and anxiety along with a sense of
   euphoria. This strain is perfect for inspiring an upbeat mood and may
   lead to conversation and creative pursuits. This plant’s flowers have a
   light sour berry and pine smell and a fresh taste similar to their
   scent. They generally have a strong blue coloring contrasted by orange
   hairs.

   [7728]black-label-kush

Black Label Kush 10G

   $24.95

   This lesser-known strain is a classic indica that provides patients
   with reliable and lengthy pain and stress relief. The effects
   transition from light and floaty to the heavy sedation typical of
   indica plants. Black Label Kush has a strong pungence bordering on the
   harsh side, but provides a rich medicating experience.
   SKU: 003Bck. Category: [7729]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [7730]Description

Product Description

   Black Label Kush
   Black Label Kush is a heavy indica that is great for sleep and
   relaxation. Black Label Kush is the type of bud that will allow you to
   slow down and not get so stressed out about the small things in life.
   Black Label Kush is a combination of two Afghani varieties and is also
   good for pain relief. Black Label Kush is not a common strain, so if
   you get your hands on it, consider yourself lucky.

   “Grade: A+

   Type: Indica

   Looks: “Medium” sized, very dense, evergreen marijuana nuggets with
   complete frosty trich coverage with areas of dark (purple) leaf
   coverage andnoticeable “rust/red hair.”

   Smell: A crisp sharp scent of pine and menthol.

   Taste: A very “rich” evergreen (and slight hint of fruitiness) danky
   mouth feel with a thick/rich hash like after taste.

   Buzz Type: A very heavy/floaty and slightly euphoric high. Provided me
   with relaxation and pain relief.

   Buzz Length: Above Average to Very Long (1.5 hours to 2+ hours)

   Summary:

   A very nice Indica strain, this batch Black Label had some super FROSTY
   marijuana nuggets. The taste was “rich” as if taking a skillet hit of
   wax. Big sniffs cleared out my nostrils as the scent was very “sharp”
   when wafting the container up to my nose.

   The first night I had a session with Black Label, I was couch locked.
   This strain gave me the feeling if eyes were “crossed.” My head felt
   “light” at the start of this buzz. The feeling I experienced is like
   “floating on clouds.” I know it’s a long time “stoner cliche,” but the
   wording does fit. The feeling of “lightness” progresses more into the
   “heavy;” especially around the eyes, about half hour after ending a
   session. This strain provided lots of “body tingle and pressure.”
   Again, this was mostly confined around the eyes and very prevalent in
   nostril area.

   Black Label was an excellent pain relief and chill out strain. This
   strain was very good at slowing my “racing mind” down. I big side
   effect was dry/sticky mouth. I did not so much get the munchies, but I
   got very thirsty with this strain. I had a big craving for sweet tea as
   I found myself in the McDonald’s drive thru many times to quench my
   thirst with their dollar sweet tea.

   Black Label is a nice strain to relax and “veg” out with and watch late
   night television while easing into a good sleep. Most of the time, I
   eased into a good nights sleep (70%) vs. being put in a state of couch
   lock (30%).”

   [7764]bluedreams_sep

Indore Blue Dream 10G

   $24.95

   Blue Dream, a sativa-dominant hybrid originating in California, has
   achieved legendary status among West Coast strains. Crossing a
   Blueberry indica with the sativa Haze, Blue Dream balances full-body
   relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration. Novice and veteran
   consumers alike enjoy the level effects of Blue Dream, which ease you
   gently into a calm euphoria. Some Blue Dream phenotypes express a more
   indica-like look and feel, but the sativa-leaning variety remains most
   prevalent.
   SKU: 004Bd. Category: [7765]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [7766]Description

Product Description

   Blue Dream

   You will find Blue Dream listed as a Sativa strain on most dispensary
   menus throughout California because of the strong, energetic head-high
   it is known for. However, digging deeper you will find that the actual
   Blue Dream genetics can be linked to Blueberry and Super Silver Haze,
   making it a 50/50 hybrid strain of cannabis. This explains why patients
   experience a nice full-body high from the Blueberry (Indica), but also
   a powerful cerebral experience from its Haze (Sativa) genetic
   counterparts.

   Blue Dream (Hybrid) Stems From Blueberry and Haze
   Being a 50/50 hybrid, you get the best of both worlds with this strain
   of cannabis. The effects are instant & plentiful, making it an instant
   favorite among most MMJ patients. However, as with all strains of
   cannabis, the specific phenotype you are medicating with is unique and
   has its own characteristics.
   For this reason, it’s important to remember that not all Blue Dream
   cuts will make you feel happy, energetic, with a soaring head-high.
   Although common, this is not always the case. Rather, depending on the
   Blue Dream phenotype, people may experience more of a full body melt
   (Indica-dominant) or uplifting head high (Sativa-dominant). It really
   depends on the specific phenotype you are medicating with. Like people,
   all strains of cannabis have their unique differences.

   Having said that, I will say that Blue Dream typically seems to have
   the same overall characteristics, regardless of phenotype. Generally
   speaking, the Blue Dream strain is popular for removing all types of
   stress and anxiety. Its calming mind-warp is a staple for the strain
   that is prominent in even the strongest Indica-dominant batches of Blue
   Dream I have come across.
   Long, thick, tan hairs are common when visually inspecting the Blue
   Dream strain. The smell is always rich, with a subtle sugar-cookie
   funk. This particular batch of Blue Dream has really frosty buds
   covered in so many sparkling trichomes that it made the overall
   appearance of the buds seem lighter in color. The vapor from the Blue
   Dream strain is super smooth, coating the entire mouth with a sweet
   blueberry sugar taste on the exhale.

   Final Thoughts About The Blue Dream Cannabis Strain
   It’s one of my go-to strains for a relaxing, thought-provoking, and
   stress-free experience. This hybrid strain seems to make the day’s
   endless list of things to do seem much more attainable. The effects
   generated from Blue Dream are typically long lasting, euphoric, and can
   be full-bodied depending on the cut of Blue Dream you have.
   Considered a personal favorite of most patients I speak to, Blue Dream
   is definitely a medical marijuana strain that is sure to grow in
   popularity for years to come.

   Chupacabra looks like a sativa and acts like an indica. With tall,
   bright green buds that fray into even brighter orange hairs, this wild
   strain reeks of its Golden Goat heritage. This strain brings together
   Hawaiian Romulan’s mental stylings with Island Sweet Skunk’s brilliant
   tropical aroma, and is finally anchored by Gupta Kush. This 50/50
   hybrid will leave your mind sizzling as you nestle into your favorite
   piece of furniture.

   system that optimizes the way your dry herbs are vaporized. It’s truly
   something special!

   The H2FLO really makes its name in the superb flow control offered by
   four unique modes of operation, allowing you to take full control over
   your entire vaporization experience. It goes beyond the standard vapor
   delivery mode (though that’s still a favorite for many!) to provide
   varying levels of strength for your vape hits.

   If you want something really special, be sure to give the water
   attachment a shot. It offers exceptional cooling for your vapor to
   create a smooth, soft yet powerful hit each time. But don’t stop there
   – using all the add-ons in tandem will result in the ultimate
   experience: with flow control, water cooling and the vapor chamber
   working together, you’ll get vapor that no other device can offer – and
   it’s all portable!

KandyPens K-Vape Micro-DX Vaporizer Pen

   $99.95
   Category: [8192]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8193]Description

Product Description

   The K-Vape Micro-DX by KandyPens is a Micro-Digital vaporizer that has
   been specially designed to utilize convection heating while remaining
   user friendly and small enough to fit in the palm of your hand. The
   K-Vape Micro-DX pen uses True Convection Technology™ meaning no
   combustion or smoke, just perfect vapor as hot air passes over the herb
   filled chamber to generate pure vapor.

   This great vape pen comes with a large anodized aluminum chamber that
   can hold up to 0.5 grams of dry herbs and has a fast heat-up time with
   over 80 available temperature settings ranging from 350°F – 430°F. The
   temperature settings can be seen on the pens digital OLED display along
   with the word heat when heating up and the word warm when the desired
   temperature has been reached. This vaporizer pen allows you to
   fine-tune your vaping experience to get that optimal heat level to
   produce thick, dense clouds with consistent results. The vape pen even
   has Smart Memory Technology that remembers your ideal settings and will
   heat the device to the last temperature used.

   For safety the K-Vape Micro-DX Pen has a 5 minute auto-shut off feature
   that ensures that your device turns off automatically to avoid any
   potentially dangerous situations. Charging the K-Vape Micro-DX has been
   made easy, simply attach the provided retractable charger cable to a
   universal USB connection and your device will start to power up
   immediately. Along with the micro USB cord, you will also find a
   cleaning brush, and a metal scoop all packed perfectly into the pens
   slide open display box.

   The K-Vape Micro-DX pen has a 3 hour battery life and is made from
   durable plastic that not only looks great, it also keeps your hands
   cool, making it even easier to hold and use. As an added bonus, this
   great dry herbal vaporizer comes with a lifetime warranty, so if you re
   looking for a top performing, portable digital vaporizer, then the
   KandyPens K-Vape Micro-DX Vaporizer is a perfect choice for new or more
   experienced vape smokers

KNOTTY BOY ALL-PURPOSE 4 OZ SHAMPOO BAR – OLIVE OIL UNSCENTED

   $7.95
   Category: [8228]Accessories.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8229]Description

Product Description

   Scent-Free 100% Olive Oil Castile, literally consisting of only
   saponified Olive Oil and Water. Castile is pure soap in its mildest
   form, ideal for ultra-sensitive skin and babies.

   Knotty Boy All Purpose Shampoo Bar is a high quality soap created using
   small batch, traditional cold-process methods and producing a
   baby-mild, creamy, high foaming bar, naturally.

   Because of this traditional process and a lack of filler ingredients,
   these big 4oz. bars are very dense, lasting up to three times longer
   than most soap bars.

   Knotty Boy All Purpose Shampoo Bar is totally SLS/chemical-free, making
   it safe for use on both tough and tender scalps, faces and skin, and is
   naturally moisturizing thanks to the restorative properties of
   certified organic Hemp Oil. It’s also ideal for travel and camping, as
   it is 100% biodegradable, mountain-stream friendly just like the Knotty
   Boy Dreadlock Shampoo Bar, and beats the heck out of carrying around
   liquid shampoo, facewash or soaps that might explode in your bag!

   [8263]SUPER-LEMON-HAZE

Lemon Haze 100G

   $199.95

   Lemon Haze has been characterized as smelling of fresh peeled lemon
   slices with a similar taste. Its buds appear to be green and yellow
   with amber hairs on the trichomes, giving it the yellow tint. This
   strain’s THC has been measured at about 15-20% with a CBD of 0.38%.
   SKU: 002Lh. Category: [8264]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8265]Description

Product Description

   Lemon Haze = Lemon Skunk x Silver Haze
   Digging a layer deeper, you will find that the Lemon Skunk found in
   Lemon Haze is a cross hatch between two Skunk plants with phenotypes
   chosen specifically for their zesty lemon characteristics. This
   explains where the lemon-peel stench comes from. With a Lemon mother,
   which has been kept in Vegas for over 20 years, and a father
   hand-picked by DNA Genetics in Holland, you know you are getting one
   heavy hitting cannabis strain.

   Additionally, the Lemon Skunk strain is known to be a good yielder that
   will grow tall with a high calyx ratio, like most Cannabis Sativa
   strains. The influence of Lemon Skunk is apparent in this batch of
   Lemon Haze, with its great smelling buds that are green with thick
   orange hairs. When I spoke with the growers, they recommended cutting
   it down between 50 – 56 days for the sweetest and tastiest cannabinoid
   profile.
   The Silver Haze strain, on the other hand, stems from a cross of Haze
   with Northern Lights and Skunk. Familiar to many as a buzzing head
   high, the Silver Haze strain is zone-inducing and extremely relaxing.
   Silver Haze gets its name from the massive amount of shiny trichomes
   covering the buds. The strong high leaves you feeling happy and clear
   headed — making it a popular choice among many patients dealing with
   anxiety disorders such as PTSD

   Flavors

   Lemon Citrus Sweet

Product Description

   of Sensi Star and Sour Diesel to create Hong Kong, which is then
   crossed with the sativa Nina Limone, a citrusy yield powerhouse. This
   gorgeous plant grows big and strong (a testament to its namesake) and
   creates buds that offer a motivating buzz with minimal paranoia. Use
   this strain as a pick-me-up that focuses the mind without encumbering
   the body.

   [8672]super-silver-haze

Super Silver Haze 5G

   $9.95

   Super Silver Haze was the first prize winner at the High Times Cannabis
   Cup in 1997, 1998, and 1999. It also won awards at the High
   Times Harvest Festival. By crossing the genetics of Skunk,Northern
   Lights, and Haze, we are left with a beautiful, sticky sativa blend
   that boasts anenergetic, long-lasting body high. The uplifting effects
   are a great remedy for high stress levels or when suffering from a lack
   of appetite or nausea.
   SKU: 001SSH. Category: [8673]Cannabis / Weed.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8674]Description

Product Description

   Super Silver Haze: (Skunk X Haze) X (Northern Lights X Haze)
   The Skunk, Northern Lights, and Haze strains combine forces to give the
   Super Silver strain star-studded genetics. It is a Sativa-dominant
   hybrid that has become one of the building blocks for superior cannabis
   since it was released in the 90’s.
   The Super Silver Haze strain really rose to fame at the end of the 20th
   Century, when it won the HIGH TIMES Cannabis Cup three years in a row.
   The strain was under the care of Green House Seeds at that point, but
   the company’s co-founders split soon thereafter.

   Since all phenotypes of cannabis strains will have different
   characteristics, it is important to remember that your batch of Super
   Silver Haze may be slightly more Indica-dominant or Sativa-dominant.
   Still, many differences are small and only noticeable to the
   experienced cannabis connoisseur.
   For instance, the terpenoid profiles will be different for each batch
   of Super Silver Haze, likely due to differences in grow environment.
   Still, this can sometimes result in a situation in which the patient
   may not know what to expect.

   The smell of Super Silver Haze can vary greatly, depending on which
   phenotype you have. Most often, the strain will be reminiscent of
   earthy haze with undertones of fruity skunk, which translates to
   pleasurable, sweet-tasting vapor that will have you excited for another
   hit.

   I’ve found that the Super Silver Haze strain often provides a whirlwind
   of energy, while producing a calming, uplifting, clear-headed feeling
   of content. For this reason, I would easily consider this one of my
   favorite Sativa-dominant hybrids to start the day.
   Super Silver Haze is considered to be good for headaches, migraines,
   and helping to manage anxiety, although more anecdotal research is
   necessary to know exactly what sort of relief it can offer each
   individual. But not to worry, we’re working on it.

   Flavors

   Sweet, Citrus, Pungent

Storz & Bickel Crafty Vaporizer

   $199.95
   Category: [8710]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8711]Description
     * [8712]Reviews (0)

Product Description

   The Crafty is a portable, battery-powered Pocket-Vaporizer. The
   Crafty’s compact construction with a single Lithium-Ion battery power
   is complemented by a practical one button control: You turn on the
   Crafty with only one keypress. It then heats up automatically until it
   reaches the default set basic temperature of 356°F (180°C). With a
   double-click on the button, you activate the booster temperature of
   383°F (195°C). When the set vaporization temperature is reached, it is
   signaled through a short double-vibration and the LED-indicator lamp:
   The LED changes the color from red to green.

   With the Crafty, vaporization functions on the basis of a full hot air
   convection heating combined with conduction. The convection heating
   provides an immediate and continuous vaporization, whereas the
   conduction ensures that there is vapor created from the very first
   breath.

   The filling chamber, which is integrated into the vaporizer, is to be
   filled with plant material (this is facilitated by the included filling
   aid) and the cooling unit with mouthpiece is to be attached. The
   cooling unit makes sure that the vapor cools down and guarantees
   optimal flavor and a rich aroma. The Crafty is the smallest Storz &
   Bickel Vaporizer with a size of 4.3 x 2.2 x 1.3 inches (11.0 x 5.7 x
   3.3 cm) and a weight of 0.3 lbs (135 g) and comes with a Crafty
   vaporizer, USB Charger, Filling aid, Grinder, Cleaning brush, Liquid
   pad, 3x spare screens, Set of spare sealing rings and Instruction
   manual.

   The free Crafty Bluetooth Remote Control App offers you the opportunity
   to set basic and booster temperature of your device according to your
   personal preferences. Amongst other things, the App allows you to read
   off the battery charge status on your smartphone, to turn on and off
   the vibration function of the Crafty and to activate an alarm and
   vibration function for your smartphone. You can download the Crafty
   Remote Control App for free from the Apple App Store or from the Google
   Play Store

Volcano Mighty Portable Vaporizer

   $150.00
   Category: [8746]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8747]Description

Product Description

   The Mighty by Storz & Bickel, is a portable, battery powered and
   dynamic Vaporizer. Due to the plus-/minus keys and the easily visible
   LED-display, the operation of the Mighty is self-explaining: As soon as
   the actual temperature corresponds to the individually adjustable set
   temperature, the device is ready for use. This is additionally
   indicated by a short double-vibration. Through the setting options
   directly on the device, the personally preferred temperature can be
   adjusted gradually during vaporization. The Mighty Vaporizer has a
   Dual-Lithium-Ion battery power, which allows a long operating life and
   a great radius of action. The Mighty can also be operated via power
   adapter with completely discharged batteries.

   With the Mighty, vaporization functions on the basis of a full hot air
   convection heating combined with conduction. The convection heating
   provides an immediate and continuous vaporization, whereas the
   conduction ensures that there is vapor created from the very first
   breath.

   You can use the included filling aid for a quick and clean filling of
   the filling chamber, which is integrated into the vaporizer. In place
   of the cooling unit, the filling aid is attached on top of the filling
   chamber. The cooling unit assures that the vapor cools down and
   guarantees an optimal flavor and a rich aroma.

   The Mighty is a portable, battery-run and powerful Vaporizer by Storz &
   Bickel with a size of 5.5 x 3.2 x 1.2 inches (14.0 x 8.0 x 3.0 cm) and
   a weight of only 0.5 lbs (235 g).

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Power Adapter
     * 1 x Liquid Pad
     * 3 x Spare Screens
     * 1 x Cleaning Brush
     * 1 x Herb Mill (Grinder)
     * 1 x Filling Aid
     * 1 x Seal Rings
     * 1 x Instruction Manual

   [8781]Capture

Volcano Plenty Vaporizer

   $199.95
   Category: [8782]Vaporizers.
   1___
   (BUTTON) Add to cart
     * [8783]Description

Product Description

   The Volcano Plenty Vaporizer is a powerful and sturdy portable device.
   The heat exchanger is equipped with a double helix to ensure efficient
   air heating and quality vaporization. The Volcano Plenty Vaporizer
   features a stainless steel cooling coil, ensuring you a pleasant
   aromatic experience.

   The temperature of the Volcano Plenty can be manually adjusted from
   130°C (266°F) to 202°C (395°F). An analog thermometer shows the
   temperature in the filling chamber, so you can always keep a close eye
   on the temperature. The Volcano Plenty’s bi-metallic regulator ensures
   safe operation, with independent temperature control and automatic
   shut-off.

The benefits of the Volcano vaporization method:

     * Effect
     * Purity
     * Flavor

   The Volcano Vaporization System releases flavors and active ingredients
   from plant material through vaporization by hot air. With the
   vaporization technique hot air passes through the plants. During this
   process the flavoring and active ingredients will be set free through
   controlled temperature 130°C (266°F) to 202°C (395°F). Due to the
   specific vaporization temperature of the plant material the ingredients
   are released into the air and can subsequently be inhaled.

   Smoking or incensing releases ingredients through heat but the
   temperature is reached through combustion which has several
   disadvantages. Smoking involves the combustion, incensing the
   carbonization of plant material, followed by the unavoidable inhalation
   of toxic combustion by-products, which cause irritation of the
   respiratory tract as well as noxious odors. In addition, the high and
   uncontrolled combustion temperature causes the unnecessary destruction
   of the majority of the ingredients, squandering the original material
   without any effect.

   Vaporizing does the opposite, the ingredients are released in a gentle
   way and therefore you enjoy both health benefits as well as economic
   benefits. The plant material doesn’t get burned and hence it is
   possible to vaporize the contents of the filling chamber several times
   until all the aroma and ingredients are completely dissolved.

   Accessories (Included):
     * 1 x Herbal Filling Chamber
     * 1 x Mouthpiece
     * 3 x Normal Screen Set
     * 2 x Tubing (Short)
     * 2 x Tubing (Long)
     * 1 x Cooling Coil
     * 1 x Liquid Pad
     * 1 x Cleaning Brush
     * 1 x Herbal Grinder
     * 1 x Instruction Manual
